<materialsCitation pageId="35" pageNumber="93">
<collectingCountry box="[905,1156,425,463]" name="Sao Tome Island" pageId="35" pageNumber="93">Sao Tomé Island</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry name="Sao Tome and Principe" pageId="35" pageNumber="93">Sao Tomé and Principe</collectingCountry>
.
</materialsCitation>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="35.[738,1330,390,817]" pageId="35" pageNumber="93">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Bocage" authorityYear="1889" box="[739,1077,508,541]" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Myonycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="35" pageNumber="93" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="brachycephala">Myonycteris brachycephala</taxonomicName>
is closely related to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Dobson" authorityYear="1878" box="[780,937,547,580]" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Myonycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="35" pageNumber="93" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="torquata">M. torquata</taxonomicName>
(separation occurred c.1-8 million years ago); it was placed in a separate subgenus (Phygetis), which has been rejected. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="35" pageNumber="93" type="distribution">
